author: Nerd of the Rings
description:
Today, we are chatting with filmmakers of the new War of the Rohirrim film!

In order of appearance:
Philippa Boyens, Producer
Phoebe Gittins & Arty Papageorgiou, Writers
Kenji Kamiyama, Director
Gaia Wise, Héra
Laurence Ubong Williams, Fréaláf

00:00-28:25 Philippa, Phoebe, & Arty (Producer, Writers)
28:25-33:47 Kenji Kamiyama (Director)
33:47-38:38 Gaia Wise & Laurence Ubong Williams (Héra & Fréaláf)

#waroftherohirrim #lordoftherings #tolkien
title: War of the Rohirrim filmmaker interviews
